'''北部省'''是[[斯里蘭卡|斯里蘭卡]]北海岸的一個省份。面積8,284平方公里。2001年人口為1,040,963人。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.statistics.gov.lk/PopHouSat/PDF/Population/p9p2%20Population%20by%20district%20,%20sex,%20sex%20ratio%20and%20population%20density.pdf |title=2001年人口普查 |accessdate=2008-04-25 |archive-date=2012-05-17 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/67j70arpb?url=http://www.statistics.gov.lk/PopHouSat/PDF/Population/p9p2%20Population%20by%20district%20%2C%20sex%2C%20sex%20ratio%20and%20population%20density.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>首府[[賈夫納|賈夫納]]。下分5區。

1987年-2006年間曾與[[東部省_(斯里蘭卡)|東部省]]組成[[東北省_(斯里蘭卡)|東北省]]，後來被裁定分離。<ref>REDDY, B. M., [http://www.hinduonnet.com/fline/fl2321/stories/20061103003002700.htm Divisive decision] {{Wayback|url=http://www.hinduonnet.com/fline/fl2321/stories/20061103003002700.htm |date=20071013161744 }}. Frontline, Volume 23 - Issue 21 :: Oct. 21-Nov. 03, 2006.</ref>

在古代，在[[斯里蘭卡|斯里蘭卡]]王的命令下在[[賈夫納|賈夫納]]的斯兵屠殺百萬[[泰米爾人|泰米爾人]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=fRjBZ2AxxyMC&pg=PA64&dq=Elara+killed++one+million+and+thirty+thousand++tamils&hl=en&sa=X&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q=Elara%20killed%20%20one%20million%20and%20thirty%20thousand%20%20tamils&f=false |title=存档副本 |access-date=2022-01-30 |archive-date=2021-12-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211227010344/https://books.google.com/books?id=fRjBZ2AxxyMC&pg=PA64&dq=Elara+killed++one+million+and+thirty+thousand++tamils&hl=en&sa=X&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q=Elara%20killed%20%20one%20million%20and%20thirty%20thousand%20%20tamils&f=false }}</ref>。


